snippet.title: Aukaat Ke Bahar - Official Trailer ft. Elvish Yadav, Nikhil Vijay, Malhaar Rathod | Amazon MX Player
snippet.description:
Amazon MX Player presents 
Aukaat Ke Bahar - Official Trailer

Starring: Elvish Yadav, Malhaar Rathod, Nikhil Vijay, Hetal Gada, Rohan Khurrana, Keshav Sadhna
Production House: Rusk Studios
Produced By: Rusk Media Pvt. Ltd.
Directed By: Tanmai Rastogi
Developed, Story, Screenplay and Written by: Jayati Pandya, Akhilesh Vats, Jasmeet Bhatia, Ayush Gaur, Sumbul Khan, Siddharth Saini

Genre: Drama Romance
 
About Aukaat Ke Bahar: Rajveer Ahlawat, a small-town boxer from Safidon, enters DelhiтАЩs elite St. Collins college to fulfill his brotherтАЩs dream of becoming a polished, English-speaking graduate. Amidst bullies, culture shocks, and class divides, he falls for Antara Shukla тАФ a senior with political aspirations and far out of his league. When a humiliating dare collides with his growing feelings and a family crisis back home, Rajveer must fight harder than ever тАФ this time, not for glory, but for love, dignity, and survival.

About Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player is IndiaтАЩs leading free, premium, ad-supported entertainment service in India. It offers a diverse range of award-winning web series, reality shows, popular international shows, and a massive movie library across multiple genres. With a strong focus on original content, Amazon MX Player has launched some of the largest shows in India, which includes Ek Badnaam Aashram, Campus Diaries, Jamnapaar, Half CA, Bhaukaal, Raktanchal, Dehati Ladke, WhoтАЩs your Gynac, Sixer, Hip Hop India, Hunter тАУ Totega Nahi Todega and more. Amazon MX Player also offers a rich selection of international content dubbed in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu under MX Vdesi, featuring popular shows like What's Wrong With Secretary Kim?, Daydreamer, Gangnam Beauty, My Girlfriend Is An Alien, Put Your Head On My Shoulder, Our Story, and more!

id.description:
Amazon MX Player mempersembahkan
Aukaat Ke Bahar - Trailer Resmi

Dibintangi: Elvish Yadav, Malhaar Rathod, Nikhil Vijay, Hetal Gada, Rohan Khurrana, Keshav Sadhna
Rumah Produksi: Rusk Studios
Diproduksi Oleh: Rusk Media Pvt. Ltd.
Disutradarai Oleh: Tanmai Rastogi
Dikembangkan, Cerita, Skenario, dan Ditulis oleh: Jayati Pandya, Akhilesh Vats, Jasmeet Bhatia, Ayush Gaur, Sumbul Khan, Siddharth Saini

Genre: Drama Romantis

Tentang Aukaat Ke Bahar: Rajveer Ahlawat, seorang petinju kota kecil dari Safidon, memasuki perguruan tinggi elit St. Collins di Delhi untuk mewujudkan impian saudaranya menjadi lulusan yang cerdas dan berbahasa Inggris. Di tengah perundungan, kejutan budaya, dan perbedaan kelas, ia jatuh cinta pada Antara Shukla тАФ seorang mahasiswa tingkat akhir dengan aspirasi politik yang jauh di luar kemampuannya. Ketika sebuah tantangan yang memalukan berbenturan dengan perasaannya yang semakin kuat dan krisis keluarga di kampung halaman, Rajveer harus berjuang lebih keras dari sebelumnya тАФ kali ini, bukan demi kejayaan, melainkan demi cinta, martabat, dan kelangsungan hidup.

Tentang Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player adalah layanan hiburan gratis, premium, dan beriklan terkemuka di India. Layanan ini menawarkan beragam serial web pemenang penghargaan, acara realitas, acara internasional populer, dan koleksi film yang sangat banyak dari berbagai genre. Dengan fokus yang kuat pada konten orisinal, Amazon MX Player telah meluncurkan beberapa acara terbesar di India, termasuk Ek Badnaam Aashram, Campus Diaries, Jamnapaar, Half CA, Bhaukaal, Raktanchal, Dehati Ladke, WhoтАЩs your Gynac, Sixer, Hip Hop India, Hunter тАУ Totega Nahi Todega, dan banyak lagi. Amazon MX Player juga menawarkan beragam pilihan konten internasional yang dialihbahasakan ke dalam bahasa Hindi, Tamil, dan Telugu di bawah naungan MX Vdesi, menampilkan acara-acara populer seperti What's Wrong With Secretary Kim?, Daydreamer, Gangnam Beauty, My Girlfriend Is An Alien, Put Your Head On My Shoulder, Our Story, dan banyak lagi!

The inspiration behind this video: 

Will Eleven get another chance at defeating Vecna? Is Max going to wake up? Can Will ever find peace in his life? These were just some of my biggest questions going into Stranger Things season 5, Volume 1. Seeing as it has been over three years since Stranger Things season 4's ending, my list of lingering questions has become overwhelmingly long. But I guess good things do come to those who wait, because Volume 1's four episodes quickly answer some of my most burning questions.

Set a year and a half after the events of season 4, Stranger Things season 5 finds Hawkins under military control following the "earthquake" that tore apart the town, which was actually caused by Vecna. The villain hasn't been seen since he was thrown from a window with a shotgun blast, but that hasn't stopped the group from staying ready for Vecna's next move. While Hopper and Joyce are helping Eleven train, Mike, Will, Dustin, Lucas, Nancy, Jonathan, Steve, and Robin coordinate ways to locate Vecna. Max is still present, but she remains in a coma, serving as a reminder about how high the stakes are.

Thank You So Much For Watching!
Stay Tuned! Stay Buzzed!

Inspirasi di balik video ini:

Akankah Eleven mendapatkan kesempatan lagi untuk mengalahkan Vecna? Akankah Max bangun? Akankah Will menemukan kedamaian dalam hidupnya? Ini hanyalah beberapa pertanyaan terbesar saya menjelang Stranger Things musim ke-5, Volume 1. Mengingat sudah lebih dari tiga tahun sejak Stranger Things musim ke-4 berakhir, daftar pertanyaan saya yang masih menggantung menjadi sangat panjang. Tapi saya rasa hal baik memang datang bagi mereka yang menunggu, karena empat episode Volume 1 dengan cepat menjawab beberapa pertanyaan saya yang paling mendesak.

Berlatar satu setengah tahun setelah peristiwa musim ke-4, Stranger Things musim ke-5 menceritakan Hawkins di bawah kendali militer setelah "gempa bumi" yang menghancurkan kota, yang sebenarnya disebabkan oleh Vecna. Penjahat itu belum terlihat sejak ia terlempar dari jendela dengan tembakan senapan, tetapi itu tidak menghentikan kelompok itu untuk tetap siap menghadapi serangan Vecna тАЛтАЛselanjutnya. Sementara Hopper dan Joyce membantu Eleven berlatih, Mike, Will, Dustin, Lucas, Nancy, Jonathan, Steve, dan Robin berkoordinasi untuk menemukan Vecna. Max masih ada, tetapi ia tetap koma, menjadi pengingat betapa tingginya taruhannya.

Terima kasih banyak telah menonton!
Tetaplah di sini! Tetaplah bersemangat!

Sung by the dynamic duo Khesari Lal Yadav and Priyanka Singh, this love track beautifully captures the essence of romance through heartfelt lyrics and soulful melodies. With its catchy composition and visually stunning official video, this Bhojpuri DJ song is quickly becoming a fan favorite across social media and music platforms.

The music video showcases a compelling love story blending traditional Bhojpuri vibes with a modern cinematic touch. Whether you're a fan of Bhojpuri cinema, love songs, or the chart-topping voice of Khesari Lal Yadav, "Disco Mein Kisko Nachaogi" is a must-watch and a must-listen.

The song revolves around a daughter complaining to her mother about her husband (Jawai) and his funny, troublesome daily activities. With R NaitтАЩs signature lyrical style and MixSinghтАЩs energetic folk-dance production, Jawai brings a perfect mix of drama, emotion and Punjabi bhangra flavour.

snippet.title: Jaan Jaan (Official Video) | Happy Raikoti | Jasmine Bhasin | Punjabi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Humble Music & Gippy Grewal present the love anthem тАЬJaan JaanтАЭ by Happy Raikoti ft. Jasmine Bhasin тЭдя╕ПтЬиiIt s a soft, romantic Punjabi song that talks about finding your true love тАФ the person who feels perfect and irreplaceable. With heartfelt lyrics and a soothing melody, the track beautifully shows the deep bond between two people who are made for each other.

Written and composed by Happy Raikoti, this song carries pure emotion and a calm, lovely vibe that touches the heart. A perfect listen for anyone who believes in real love.
